snippet.title: Alchemic Cutie Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Alchemic Cutie is a relaxing adventure RPG set on colorful Wimba Island. While taming wild jellies, you’ll meet villagers, enter jelly compeitions and uncover the secrets of the island.

Sign up for the alpha @ alchemiccutie.com/alpha

Website: https://alchemiccutie.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/913720/Alchemic_Cutie/
Itch: https://alchemiccutie.itch.io/game
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/alchemiccutie/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/alchemiccutie
